            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>AVIOT 一向以高性价比的真无线蓝牙耳机闻名，这次推出的 WA-Q1 真无线降噪耳机延续此优势，并号称全球最细巧的头戴式降噪耳机，定价仅港币 599 元。这款耳机具备 55 小时超长续航，还配备混合降噪功能，能有效隔绝外界噪音，让用家专注享受音乐。以下就由小编带大家开箱，一睹这款平价实用的入门级耳机真面目吧！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00220-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00220-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00220.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>糖果色系机身，容易衬衫时尚百搭</h2><p>AVIOT WA-Q1 的外观设计别具一格，令人眼前一亮。精致的造型让人难以联想到其售价仅为 599 元。耳机外露的连接线加入了复古元素，而多款糖果色选择则赋予产品青春活力。用家可选择黑、粉蓝、粉红或灰色，小编测试的是粉红版本，甜美亮眼，轻易衬托不同穿搭风格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00227-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00227-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00227.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 糖果色系，视觉年轻化</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00224-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00224-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00224.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲外露耳机线，融入复古元素</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00264-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00264-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00264.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲收纳时需小心保护电线，避免损坏</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00228-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00228-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc00228.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头带刻有「AVIOT」字样，增添品牌辨识度</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1284574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc002522-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><br /><b>
